# Frontend Project Structure

This is a modern Next.js 15 frontend application using React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui components for the InterviewInsight AI platform.

## Project Structure

```
frontend/
├── src/
│   ├── app/                   # Next.js App Router
│   │   ├── layout.tsx        # Root layout
│   │   ├── page.tsx          # Homepage
│   │   ├── analysis/         # Analysis results page
│   │   └── api/              # API routes (backend proxy)
│   ├── components/            # React components
│   │   ├── ui/               # shadcn/ui components
│   │   ├── transcript-analyzer.tsx  # Main analysis interface
│   │   ├── analysis-dashboard.tsx   # Results dashboard
│   │   └── ...               # Other app components
│   ├── types/                # TypeScript definitions
│   ├── lib/                  # Utility functions
│   └── styles/               # Global styles
├── public/                   # Static assets
└── package.json              # Dependencies and scripts
```

## Key Components

- **App Router**: Next.js 15 App Router with TypeScript
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui component library with Radix UI
- **Transcript Analyzer**: Main AI-powered analysis interface
- **Analysis Dashboard**: Results visualization and display
- **Type Safety**: Full TypeScript coverage with strict mode
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4.0 with CSS variables
